HEADWORD: Geomalism
<hw>Ge*om"a*lism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>ge`a</grk>, <grk>gh^</grk>, the earth + <grk>"omalismo`s</grk> a
leveling.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>The tendency of an organism to
